        "content": "<p>Hey all, a little xmas present for you: I have added support for making the heirarchical table displays in the specification active:</p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/10155/epn9VtSn8RiDe15KWYcheyan/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pasted_image.png\">pasted image</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/10155/epn9VtSn8RiDe15KWYcheyan/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pasted image\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/10155/epn9VtSn8RiDe15KWYcheyan/pasted_image.png\"></a></div><p>click on the icon, get: </p>\n<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/10155/HpEdCfLvoEvS5Q1aFgqpZelr/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pasted_image.png\">pasted image</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/10155/HpEdCfLvoEvS5Q1aFgqpZelr/pasted_image.png\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"pasted image\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/10155/HpEdCfLvoEvS5Q1aFgqpZelr/pasted_image.png\"></a></div>",
        "id": 183505557,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1576445656
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Your actions are remembered during a session.</p>",
        "id": 183505566,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1576445678
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>you can have this too, in your IGs, if you are building IGs. To get this in an IG, you need to do 2 things:</p>\n<p>First, you have to add this entry in your html header:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>  <span class=\"p\">&lt;</span><span class=\"nt\">script</span> <span class=\"na\">src</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;fhir-table-scripts.js&quot;</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span class=\"nt\">script</span><span class=\"p\">&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>",
        "id": 183505598,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1576445762
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>you have add this to your header (before any of the tables in the page), not the footer (which is usual practice)</p>",
        "id": 183505630,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1576445778
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>and you have to tell the IG publisher that you've done this: </p>\n<p>for the old ig.json approach:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>  <span class=\"s2\">&quot;activeTables&quot;</span> <span class=\"err\">:</span> <span class=\"kc\">true</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>and in the new IG approach:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>   <span class=\"nt\">&lt;parameter&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"nt\">&lt;code</span> <span class=\"na\">value=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;active-tables&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n     <span class=\"nt\">&lt;value</span> <span class=\"na\">value=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;true&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/parameter&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>Or it's equivalent in json.</p>\n<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"191320\">@Lloyd McKenzie</span> can you add this to the standard template please</p>",
        "id": 183505714,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1576445972
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>see it at work here: <a href=\"http://build.fhir.org/patient.html\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"http://build.fhir.org/patient.html\">http://build.fhir.org/patient.html</a></p>",
        "id": 183505760,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1576446004
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Will do.  (And thank you for the Christmas present :))</p>",
